title: The Winnipeg Jets Fall To The Minnesota Wild As Injuries And Fatigue Continue To Mount
creator: Locked On Jets - Daily Podcast On The Winnipeg Jets
subject: Podcast
description: On tonight's episode, we recap a dispiriting loss to the Minnesota Wild. Were the Jets truly as bad as the 4-1 scoreline might imply? What positive takeaways can Winnipeg fans latch on to? Is there any help in sight for a Jets team struggling to ice 4 competitive lines? Just how bad has the roster depth been to have the current Jets line-up in this state? When will the front office decide to make a roster move? Are there any forward candidates the Jets can acquire to turn the tide, or will it fail to be enough to move the needle?
